&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Familiarity with cloud and containerisation technologies, test automation tools and CI/CD pipelines&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:0}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
